Part 31", "96": "31.6, Disclosure and Inspection of Documents, Part 31", "97": "31.7, Disclosure and Inspection of Documents, Part 31", "98": "31.8, Disclosure and Inspection of Documents, Part 31", "99": "31.9, Disclosure and Inspection of Documents, Part 31"}, "data_points": {"images": null, "text": [{"category": "Civil Procedure Rules and Practice Directions", "citation": "1.1, Disclosure for the Business and Property Courts, Practice Direction 57A", "content": "1.1 This Practice Direction provides for disclosure in the Business and Property Courts.", "filepath": "Disclosure for the Business and Property Courts", "groups": [], "id": "Practice_Direction_57AD___Disclosure_for_the_Business_and_Property_Courts_chunk_001_subsection_0", "is_subsection": true, "oids": [], "original_doc_id": "Practice_Direction_57AD___Disclosure_for_the_Business_and_Property_Courts_chunk_001", "reranker_score": 2.6706557273864746, "score": 0.022727273404598236, "sourcefile": "Practice Direction 57A", "sourcepage": "Disclosure for the Business and Property Courts", "storageUrl": "https://www.justice.gov.uk/courts/procedure-rules/civil/rules/part-57a-business-and-property-courts/practice-direction-57ad-disclosure-in-the-business-and-property-courts", "storageurl": "https://www.justice.gov.uk/courts/procedure-rules/civil/rules/part-57a-business-and-property-courts/practice-direction-57ad-disclosure-in-the-business-and-property-courts", "subsection_id": "1.1", "subsection_index": 0, "total_subsections": 67, "updated": "2022-09-29T00:00:00Z", "url": "https://www.justice.gov.uk/courts/procedure-rules/civil/rules/part-57a-business-and-property-courts/practice-direction-57ad-disclosure-in-the-business-and-property-courts"}, {"category": "King's Bench Division", "citation": "1.2, Disclosure for the Business and Property Courts, Practice Direction 57A", "content": "1.2 The Commencement Date is 1 October 2022. This Practice Direction applies to existing and new proceedings in the Business and Property Courts of England and Wales and the Business and Property Courts in Birmingham, Bristol, Cardiff, Leeds, Liverpool, Manchester and Newcastle. For the avoidance of doubt, it does not apply in the County Court. This Practice Direction is substantially in the form of (and replaces) Practice Direction 51 U.", "filepath": "Disclosure for the Business and Property Courts", "groups": [], "id": "Practice_Direction_57AD___Disclosure_for_the_Business_and_Property_Courts_chunk_001_subsection_1", "is_subsection": true, "oids": [], "original_doc_id": "Practice_Direction_57AD___Disclosure_for_the_Business_and_Property_Courts_chunk_001", "reranker_score": 2.6706557273864746, "score": 0.022727273404598236, "sourcefile": "35.16_JO_Kings_Bench_Division_Guide_2025_WEB4.pdf", "sourcepage": "4. Applications made pre-issue or at the point of issue (p. 41)", "storageUrl": "https://www.justice.gov.uk/courts/procedure-rules/civil/rules/part-57a-business-and-property-courts/practice-direction-57ad-disclosure-in-the-business-and-property-courts", "storageurl": "https://www.judiciary.uk/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/35.16_JO_Kings_Bench_Division_Guide_2025_WEB4.pdf", "subsection_id": "1.2", "subsection_index": 1, "total_subsections": 67, "updated": "2025-04-01T00:00:00Z", "url": "https://www.justice.gov.uk/courts/procedure-rules/civil/rules/part-57a-business-and-property-courts/practice-direction-57ad-disclosure-in-the-business-and-property-courts"}, {"category": "Civil Procedure Rules and Practice Directions", "citation": "1.3, Disclosure for the Business and Property Courts, Practice Direction 57A", "content": "1.3 This Practice Direction shall not disturb an order for disclosure made before the Commencement Date or before the transfer of proceedings into a Business and Property Court, unless that order is varied or set aside. If proceedings are transferred out of one of the Business and Property Courts into a court that is not one of the Business and Property Courts, any order for disclosure made under this Practice Direction will stand unless and until any other order is made by the transferee court.", "filepath": "Disclosure for the Business and Property Courts", "groups": [], "id": "Practice_Direction_57AD___Disclosure_for_the_Business_and_Property_Courts_chunk_001_subsection_2", "is_subsection": true, "oids": [], "original_doc_id": "Practice_Direction_57AD___Disclosure_for_the_Business_and_Property_Courts_chunk_001", "reranker_score": 2.6706557273864746, "score": 0.022727273404598236, "sourcefile": "Part 31", "sourcepage": "Disclosure and Inspection of Documents", "storageUrl": "https://www.justice.gov.uk/courts/procedure-rules/civil/rules/part-57a-business-and-property-courts/practice-direction-57ad-disclosure-in-the-business-and-property-courts", "storageurl": "https://www.justice.gov.uk/courts/procedure-rules/civil/rules/part31", "subsection_id": "1.3", "subsection_index": 2, "total_subsections": 67, "updated": "2024-04-06T00:00:00Z", "url": "https://www.justice.gov.uk/courts/procedure-rules/civil/rules/part-57a-business-and-property-courts/practice-direction-57ad-disclosure-in-the-business-and-property-courts"}, {"category": "Civil Procedure Rules and Practice Directions", "citation": "1.4, Disclosure for the Business and Property Courts, Practice Direction 57A", "content": "1.4 This Practice Direction shall not, unless otherwise ordered, apply to proceedings which are-

(1) a Competition claim as defined in Practice Direction 31 C;

(2) a Public Procurement claim;

(3) within the Intellectual Property and Enterprise Court;

(4) within the Admiralty Court;

(5) within the Shorter and Flexible Trials Schemes;

(6) within a fixed costs regime or a capped costs regime; or

(7) claims proceeding under Part 8.", "filepath": "Disclosure for the Business and Property Courts", "groups": [], "id": "Practice_Direction_57AD___Disclosure_for_the_Business_and_Property_Courts_chunk_001_subsection_3", "is_subsection": true, "oids": [], "original_doc_id": "Practice_Direction_57AD___Disclosure_for_the_Business_and_Property_Courts_chunk_001", "reranker_score": 2.6706557273864746, "score": 0.022727273404598236, "sourcefile": "Practice Direction 57A", "sourcepage": "Disclosure for the Business and Property Courts", "storageUrl": "https://www.justice.gov.uk/courts/procedure-rules/civil/rules/part-57a-business-and-property-courts/practice-direction-57ad-disclosure-in-the-business-and-property-courts", "storageurl": "https://www.justice.gov.uk/courts/procedure-rules/civil/rules/part-57a-business-and-property-courts/practice-direction-57ad-disclosure-in-the-business-and-property-courts", "subsection_id": "1.4", "subsection_index": 3, "total_subsections": 67, "updated": "2022-09-29T00:00:00Z", "url": "https://www.justice.gov.uk/courts/procedure-rules/civil/rules/part-57a-business-and-property-courts/practice-direction-57ad-disclosure-in-the-business-and-property-courts"}, {"category": "Civil Procedure Rules and Practice Directions", "citation": "1.5, Disclosure for the Business and Property Courts, Practice Direction 57A", "content": "1.5 In the Patents Court, PD 63 paragraphs 6.1 to 6.3 will continue to apply under this Practice Direction with the following modification: unless the court expressly orders otherwise, no provision in this practice direction nor any disclosure order made under this Practice Direction will take effect as requiring disclosure wider than is provided for in PD 63 paragraph 6.1.", "filepath": "Disclosure for the Business and Property Courts", "groups": [], "id": "Practice_Direction_57AD___Disclosure_for_the_Business_and_Property_Courts_chunk_001_subsection_4", "is_subsection": true, "oids": [], "original_doc_id": "Practice_Directi